name: Mornings w/ MetaDad & The Coffee Cup Club

metadata.name: Cups
metadata.description:
Mornings w/ MetaDad & The Coffee Cup Club celebrate the 300th episode of their morning Twitter Space show. 

This NFT is a momentum and symbolises the growth of the amazing community members that tune in each morning to share GM's and good vibes for good people. 

By owning this NFT you share a part of the journey of their growth through web3, a permanent moment of history on the blockchain.
